oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Historic brick townhouse at 1235 Sixth Avenue in, Nashville, Tennessee, circa 1968
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An historic brick townhouse at 1235 Sixth Avenue in the historic Germantown district, Nashville, Tennessee, circa 1968. After renovation, this structure later became Monell’s Dining and Catering. Forms part of Record Group 3. The original is a 35 mm color transparency (2 x 2 in. slide mount).
